{"type": "article", "id": 21801, "title": "CULTEAVO TEA by Robinsson Cravents", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-03T08:14:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153117uxLsqf0D6UdRpOmg.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组茶叶都用锡罐作为包装，一共有 6 种。每一个罐子上的都有小鸟、树叶、蜗牛、蝴蝶等自然图案，是根据圆点之间疏密关系排列出来，有立体感，是素描的手法。图案上的 6 个彩色圆点区分了茶叶的不同的品种，它们出现的位置相同。而罐子下面的白色标签则写清了使用方式，都使包装显得素雅。<br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153115QqTi5zfgGu1r2vXn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061531161jkHbGOpePf37arT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153116S4nDECHBjIl9s173.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153117761z0PcuOg9x5XNa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}